# Exclude markdown ONLY at the package root (READMEs etc.), NOT the bundled vault.
# An UNANCHORED `*.md` (.gitignore glob semantics) matches at EVERY depth, which
# would strip negotiate/content/**/*.md — the verbatim vault the Function reads at
# runtime — from the deploy package (empty map -> 404 for every markdown request,
# Critical #2). Anchor to the root and explicitly KEEP the bundled vault.
/*.md
!negotiate/content/
